@genryxy when I said about in-lining these methods I meant that we can just put an if {...} here and it would be more simple and less verbose:
if (user.isPresent()) {
  cmdlst.add("--user");
  cmdlst.add(String.format(...));
}
or even
user.ifPresent(
  usr -> {
    cmdlst.add("--user");
    cmdlst.add(String.format(...));
  }
)

